[package] name = "Notepad" version = "0.1.0" authors = ["Juan Leo"] edition = "2024" description = "A simple notepad application built with eframe and egui." license = "MIT" repository = "https://github.com/JuanLeo83/NotepadR" publish = false
[dependencies] eframe = { version = "0.32.2", features = ["wgpu"] } egui_extras = { version = "0.32.2", features = ["default", "image"] } env_logger = { version = "0.11.8", default-features = false, features = [ "auto-color", "humantime", ] } log = "0.4.28" rfd = "0.15.4" serde = { version = "1.0.219", features = ["derive"] } serde_json = "1.0.143" dirs = "6.0.0"
